Android application to manage all your online transactions and offline expenses. This app automatically tracks your expenses when you receive a spend related SMS.


Features:

1. Add an expense manually in the 'Add New' tab.
2. In the 'Set limit' tab, set the amount you want to spend within a time period and the beginning and end dates of that period. App will notify when that limit is reached.
3. Current status of limit, ie. amount spend, days remaining and amount safe to spend, is displayed on home screen in an attractive interface.
4. View all expenses in monthly tabulated form in 'All Expenses' tab.
5. 'Offers Tab' shows any current offer available. App reads discounts/offers received through SMS.
6. Edit/Delete any previous expense.


